Thanks [~leftnoteasy] - although, I'm starting to question if this is the right fix. It looks the test started failing after YARN-8111.

In {{PlacementConstraintTransformations}} I see null is explicitly set on the returned constraint. Should this be SELF? I think not, but [~kkaranasos] [~cheersyang] could you comment?
{code}
    @Override
    public AbstractConstraint visit(CardinalityConstraint constraint) {
      return new SingleConstraint(constraint.getScope(),
          constraint.getMinCardinality(), constraint.getMaxCardinality(),
          new TargetExpression(TargetExpression.TargetType.ALLOCATION_TAG, null,
              constraint.getAllocationTags()));
    }
{code}
